<item>
            <title>[HBASE-4401] Record log region splits and region moves in the HLog</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4401</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It would be nice to record a region splits, region close and region open in the transaction log. This will help in  in-order delivery of changes for HBase cluster replication.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
